&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;AI Instructor – Specialization in Business &amp;amp; Finance Applications&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About Wall Street Prep&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Founded in 2004 by investment bankers, Wall Street Prep (WSP) is a leading provider of professional skills training in financial and valuation modeling. Our mission is to bridge the gap between academia and the real world by equipping finance professionals and students with practical, hands-on skills.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We partner with top-tier investment banks, private equity and investment management firms, Fortune 500 companies, and elite undergraduate and MBA programs. Our training is delivered through engaging in-person classroom sessions and via our industry-leading online learning platform, all designed by experienced finance professionals.&lt;/p&gt;
